# CoreInventory IMS вЂ” Implementation Plan

A modular **Inventory Management System (IMS)** that fully digitizes and centralizes stock operations вЂ” replacing manual registers, Excel sheets, and scattered tracking. Built for two user personas: **Inventory Managers** and **Warehouse Staff**.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a **frontend-only SPA** (Single Page Application) with a simulated backend using **Zustand + LocalStorage**. No real backend/database is included. If you want a real Odoo backend integration or a Node.js/Python API, please confirm so we can adjust the plan.

> [!WARNING]
> The project will be scaffolded fresh inside `c:\Users\somes\OneDrive\Desktop\CoreInventory-Odoo-2026`. The empty git repo there will be re-used. All existing files (only `README.md`) will be preserved.

---

## Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Build Tool | **Vite 5** + React 18 + TypeScript | Fastest DX in 2026, HMR, tree-shaking |
| Routing | **React Router v7** | File-based + nested layouts |
| State | **Zustand v5** | Lightweight, scalable, with persistence middleware |
| 3D Engine | **Three.js + React Three Fiber + Drei** | GPU-accelerated 3D scenes & particles |
| Animations | **Framer Motion v11** | Spring physics, layout animations, exit animations |
| Charts | **Recharts v2** | Composable, animated charts |
| Styling | **Vanilla CSS + CSS Variables** | Full control, glassmorphism, dark theme |
| Icons | **Lucide React** | Clean, consistent icon set |
| Typography | **Inter + Space Grotesk** (Google Fonts) | Premium modern feel |
| Notifications | **React Hot Toast** | Elegant toast system |
| Date | **date-fns** | Lightweight date utilities |

---

## Design Philosophy вЂ” 2026 Aesthetic

The UI is built around a **dark glassmorphism design language** with these pillars:

- **3D Hero Elements**: Three.js canvas for login background (floating warehouse particles), dashboard 3D KPI globe
- **Glassmorphism Cards**: `backdrop-filter: blur()` + translucent borders + inner glow
- **Micro-animations**: Every interaction has a spring-physics response via Framer Motion
- **Ambient Gradients**: Deep navy в†’ violet в†’ teal color palette (`#0A0E1A в†’ #1a1040 в†’ #0d2d3d`)
- **Kinetic Typography**: Animated counters, staggered list entrances
- **Status Glow**: Badge colors emit `box-shadow` glow matching their semantic color
- **Hover Depth**: Cards lift with `translateY` + shadow depth on hover

