## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1 вЂ” Project Scaffolding

#### [NEW] Project root вЂ” `package.json`, `vite.config.ts`, `tsconfig.json`

- Scaffold via `npm create vite@latest . -- --template react-ts`
- Install: `@react-three/fiber`, `@react-three/drei`, `three`, `framer-motion`, `zustand`, `react-router-dom`, `recharts`, `lucide-react`, `react-hot-toast`, `date-fns`

---

### Phase 2 вЂ” Design System & Layout Shell

#### [NEW] `src/index.css`

Global CSS variables establishing the design system:
- Color palette: deep space navy + violet + teal gradients
- Glassmorphism mixins: `--glass-bg`, `--glass-border`, `--glass-blur`
- Typography scale (Inter for body, Space Grotesk for headings)
- All animation timing curves
- Custom scrollbar styles

#### [NEW] `src/components/layout/AppShell.tsx`

Persistent layout wrapper rendered for all authenticated pages:
- **Sidebar**: Collapsible animated nav with icon + label, active route highlight with sliding indicator, section grouping (Dashboard / Products / Operations / History / Settings)
- **TopBar**: Global search bar, warehouse switcher dropdown, notification bell with badge, user avatar + dropdown (My Profile / Logout)
- Page content area with smooth fade transitions via Framer Motion `AnimatePresence`

---

### Phase 3 вЂ” Authentication Module

#### [NEW] `src/pages/auth/LoginPage.tsx`

- Full-screen dark canvas with **Three.js ParticleField** (floating boxes/shelves in 3D space)
- Glassmorphism login card with **3D card flip** on load (Framer Motion `rotateY`)
- Email + Password form with animated label float
- "Remember me" toggle
- Link to forgot password

#### [NEW] `src/pages/auth/ResetPasswordPage.tsx`

- 3-step animated progress: **Email в†’ OTP Verify в†’ New Password**
- Framer Motion slide transitions between steps
- OTP digit input boxes with auto-focus leap
- Success confetti burst on completion

#### [NEW] `src/store/authStore.ts`

- Zustand store with `user`, `isAuthenticated`, `login()`, `logout()`, `resetPassword()`
- Persisted to localStorage

---

### Phase 4 вЂ” Dashboard Module

#### [NEW] `src/pages/dashboard/DashboardPage.tsx`

**KPI Row** (5 cards, each with):
- Animated number counter (0 в†’ value on mount with spring easing)
- Glassmorphism card with gradient icon background
- Trend delta indicator (+/- vs yesterday)
- KPIs: Total Products, Low Stock Items, Pending Receipts, Pending Deliveries, Internal Transfers

**Charts Row**:
- `StockTrendChart` вЂ” Recharts AreaChart (30-day stock level trend)
- `CategoryDonut` вЂ” Recharts PieChart with animated segments + legend
- `OperationsBar` вЂ” Recharts BarChart (Receipts vs Deliveries per week)

**Dynamic Filter Bar**:
- Pill-based filter toggles for: Document Type (Receipts / Delivery / Internal / Adjustments), Status (Draft / Waiting / Ready / Done / Cancelled), Warehouse, Category
- Filters animate in with stagger, active filters glow violet

**Alert Panel** (right column):
- Low stock items list with product name, current qty, reorder level
- Color-coded urgency (red = 0 stock, amber = below reorder point)
- Animated pulse on critical items

---

### Phase 5 вЂ” Product Management Module

#### [NEW] `src/pages/products/ProductsPage.tsx`

- Searchable, filterable data table (SKU, Name, Category, UoM, Stock, Reorder Level, Status)
- Column sorting with animated sort indicator arrows
- Row hover lift effect
- Create Product button в†’ opens `ProductForm` in sliding drawer panel
- Low stock badge glows red/amber

#### [NEW] `src/pages/products/ProductForm.tsx`

Sliding drawer form (right side overlay) with:
- Name, SKU/Code, Category (dropdown), Unit of Measure, Initial Stock
- Reordering Rule toggle в†’ Min Qty / Max Qty fields appear with smooth expansion
- Stock by location breakdown table (read-only, for edit mode)
- Save / Cancel with spring animation

---

### Phase 6 вЂ” Operations Module

#### [NEW] Receipts вЂ” `src/pages/operations/ReceiptsPage.tsx` + `ReceiptForm.tsx`

**List Page**:
- Table: Receipt #, Supplier, Date, Items Count, Status, Actions
- Status filter pills, date range picker
- Quick stats bar: total pending count, total items expected

**Form** (Create / View / Validate):
- Supplier name field, scheduled date
- Line items table: Product (searchable dropdown) + Expected Qty + Received Qty columns
- Add/remove lines dynamically (animated row insertion)
- Validate button в†’ status transitions to Done, stock auto-increments, move logged
- Status workflow badge: `Draft в†’ Waiting в†’ Ready в†’ Done` with animated step indicator

#### [NEW] Delivery Orders вЂ” `src/pages/operations/DeliveryPage.tsx` + `DeliveryForm.tsx`

Same pattern as Receipts but with:
- Customer name + destination location
- Pick в†’ Pack в†’ Validate 3-step workflow with animated stepper
- Validate в†’ stock auto-decrements

#### [NEW] Internal Transfers вЂ” `src/pages/operations/TransfersPage.tsx` + `TransferForm.tsx`

- Source Location в†’ Destination Location selector (both within warehouse hierarchy)
- Line items with product + quantity
- Validate в†’ moves stock between locations (total unchanged), logs move

#### [NEW] Inventory Adjustments вЂ” `src/pages/operations/AdjustmentsPage.tsx` + `AdjustmentForm.tsx`

- Product + Location selector
- System Quantity (read-only) vs Counted Quantity (editable)
- Delta auto-calculated and displayed (highlighted red/green)
- Validate в†’ system qty updated, adjustment logged in history

---

### Phase 7 вЂ” Move History (Stock Ledger)

#### [NEW] `src/pages/history/MoveHistoryPage.tsx`

- Full paginated ledger table: Date, Product, From Location, To Location, Qty, Operation Type, Reference, User
- Advanced filter panel: date range, product search, location, operation type
- Timeline view toggle: switches from table to animated vertical timeline
- Export to CSV button
- Each row expands to show full operation details

---

### Phase 8 вЂ” Settings Module

#### [NEW] `src/pages/settings/WarehousePage.tsx`

- List of warehouses with status toggle (active/inactive)
- Create warehouse в†’ name, short code, address
- Warehouse detail: nested location tree (visualized as animated accordion)
- Add locations (e.g., Main Store, Rack A, Production Floor)

#### [NEW] `src/pages/settings/ProfilePage.tsx`

- Avatar upload with preview + circular crop
- Edit display name, email
- Change password form with current password verification
- Active sessions / last login info

---

### Phase 9 вЂ” State & Data Layer

#### [NEW] `src/store/productStore.ts`
- CRUD for products + categories
- Low stock computed selector

#### [NEW] `src/store/operationStore.ts`
- Receipts, Deliveries, Transfers, Adjustments arrays
- `validateReceipt()`, `validateDelivery()`, `validateTransfer()`, `validateAdjustment()` вЂ” each mutates product stock and appends to `historyStore`

#### [NEW] `src/store/warehouseStore.ts`
- Warehouses + nested locations tree

#### [NEW] `src/store/historyStore.ts`
- Immutable append-only move log

#### [NEW] `src/data/mockData.ts`
- Seed with 20+ products across 5 categories, 3 warehouses, 50+ historical moves, pending receipts/deliveries

