   - Start dev server: `npm run dev` in `c:\Users\somes\OneDrive\Desktop\CoreInventory-Odoo-2026`
   - Navigate to `http://localhost:5173`
   - Login with demo credentials
   - Verify Dashboard KPIs load with animated counters
   - Create a Receipt в†’ validate в†’ check stock increased on Products page
   - Create a Delivery в†’ validate в†’ check stock decreased
   - Create an Internal Transfer в†’ validate в†’ check location updated
   - Create an Adjustment в†’ validate в†’ check move logged in History

2. **UI/Animation Testing**:
   - Verify 3D particle field renders on Login page
   - Verify sidebar collapse/expand animation
   - Verify KPI counter spring animation on Dashboard
   - Verify chart renders without errors

### Manual Verification
- Run `npm run build` and verify zero TypeScript/build errors
- Check browser console for zero runtime errors after full flow test
